OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773256283
OL,3,CWalsall sack head coach Mat Sadler
OL,4,Cafter third defeat in a row
OL,6,FWalsall have sacked head coach Mat
OL,7,FSadler after a poor run of form which
OL,8,Fsees the club out of the play-off
OL,9,Fspots for promotion.
OL,11,FThe Saddlers were once favourites for
OL,12,Fpromotion from League Two, now that
OL,13,Flooks more unlikely. The club sits in
OL,14,F11th place in League Two.
OL,16,FHis dismissal follows a 1-0 defeat to
OL,17,FSalford on Tuesday (10 March) - the
OL,18,Fclub's third defeat in a row.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
