PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773256283
OL,3,CWalsall sack head coach Mat Sadler
OL,4,Cafter third defeat in a row
OL,6,FCoach Darren Byfield will take interim
OL,7,Fcharge of the team with the immediate
OL,8,Ffocus on Saturday's fixture against
OL,9,FCrewe Alexandra.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Walsall co-chairman
OL,12,FBen Boycott said: "I would like to
OL,13,Ftake the opportunity to acknowledge
OL,14,Fthe significant efforts and
OL,15,Fcontributions of Mat, both as a
OL,16,Fprofessional and as a person, during
OL,17,Fhis time at the club.
OL,19,F"We thank him for his dedicated
OL,20,Fservice and wish him the very best for
OL,21,Fthe future."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773256283
OL,3,CWalsall sack head coach Mat Sadler
OL,4,Cafter third defeat in a row
OL,6,FThe club also said it will be working
OL,7,Fthrough next steps and will provide
OL,8,Fupdates on a new Head Coach in due
OL,9,Fcourse.
OL,11,FSadler spent three years in charge of
OL,12,FThe Saddlers and led the team to the
OL,13,Fplay-offs last year, having missed out
OL,14,Fon automatic promotion in the last
OL,15,Fgame of the season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
