PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773256283
OL,3,CWalsall sack head coach Mat Sadler
OL,4,Cafter third defeat in a row
OL,6,FHe had led the club to a record nine
OL,7,Fconsecutive league victories, although
OL,8,Fmany fans had hoped to be in
OL,9,Fcontention for automatic promotion
OL,10,Fthis season, something that seems out
OL,11,Fof reach at this point in the season.
OL,13,FAs head coach, Sadler achieved the
OL,14,Fhighest win rate of any manager at
OL,15,FWalsall for 25 years and led the club
OL,16,Fto many successes - famously holding
OL,17,FLeicester City to a goalless draw in
OL,18,Fthe third round of the FA Cup before
OL,19,Flosing on penalties.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
